nodes.documentation:
@title ChronoBank Asset With Fee implementation contract.
 * Asset implementation contract that takes percent fee on top of every transfer.
Fee amount is always rounded up.
 * Note: all the non constant functions return false instead of throwing in case if state change
didn't happen yet.
nodes.name: ChronoBankAssetWithFee

nodes.documentation: Allows the call if fee was successfully taken, throws if the call failed in the end.
nodes.name: takeFee

nodes.documentation:
Sets fee collecting address and fee percent.
     * @param _feeAddress fee collecting address.
@param _feePercent fee percent, 1 is 0.01%, 10000 is 100%.
     * @return success.
nodes.name: setupFee
setFeeAddress

nodes.documentation:
@dev Sets fee percent value. Can be changed multiple times
    * @param _feePercent fee percent, 1 is 0.01%, 10000 is 100%.
nodes.name: setFee

nodes.documentation:
Passes execution into modified function with function-modifier partially shared scope.
     * @return success.
nodes.name: _transferWithReference
_transferWithReference

nodes.documentation:
Passes execution into modified function with function-modifier partially shared scope.
     * @return success.
nodes.name: _transferFromWithReference
_transferFromWithReference
_transferFee
_subjectToFees

nodes.documentation:
Return fee that needs to be taken based on specified amount.
     * Fee amount is always rounded up.
     * @return fee amount.
nodes.name: calculateFee
